  <title>Pin-Joint</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Definition<keyword>Hinge Joint</keyword><keyword>Pin-Joint</keyword><keyword>Pivot Point</keyword><keyword>Revolute Joint</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="2" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:158px;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-Pop-GA-PinJointSym-PU.png" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[2 x Pin-Joints]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Element">Pin-Joint -</text> a joint between two <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Sketch-Element-Point" styleclass="Element">Points</link> in two different <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">parts</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Parts</text> rotate relative to each other.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Symbols" styleclass="VariableName-small">Symbols</link><text styleclass="Popup Box"> for a </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Pin-Joint</text><text styleclass="Popup Box">:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:6pt; vertical-align:sub;" figurelistinclude="0"></image>&#32;<text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Circle - </text>it moves relative to the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Base-Part</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Normal"> -</text>&#32;<text styleclass="VariableName-small">POS Geometric Drawing Symbol</text> - it cannot move relative to the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Base-Part</text>.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Pin-Joint</text> is also known as a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Revolute Joint</text>, or a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Hinge Joint</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Slide-Joint">Slide-Joint</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Ball-Joints">Ball-Joint</link>, <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddPinJoint">Add Pin-Joint</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
